      "rendered": "\n\u003Cfigure class=\"wp-block-image size-medium is-resized\"\u003E\u003Cimg data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" data-attachment-id=\"6068\" data-permalink=\"https://blog.vrid.in/2025/03/04/budget-2025-new-income-tax-bill-all-key-changes-explained/tax-bro-4/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/blog.vrid.in/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Tax-bro.png?fit=2000%2C2000&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2000,2000\" data-comments-opened=\"0\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Tax-bro\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/blog.vrid.in/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Tax-bro.png?fit=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/blog.vrid.in/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Tax-bro.png?fit=1024%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/blog.vrid.in/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Tax-bro.png?resize=300%2C300&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"Budget 2025 &amp; New Income Tax Bill: All Key Changes Explained | Vrid\" class=\"wp-image-6068\" style=\"object-fit:contain;width:300px;height:300px\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/blog.vrid.in/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Tax-bro.png?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/blog.vrid.in/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Tax-bro.png?resize=1024%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/blog.vrid.in/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Tax-bro.png?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/blog.vrid.in/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Tax-bro.png?resize=768%2C768&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/blog.vrid.in/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Tax-bro.png?resize=1536%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/blog.vrid.in/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Tax-bro.png?resize=1200%2C1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/blog.vrid.in/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Tax-bro.png?resize=800%2C800&amp;ssl=1 800w, https://i0.wp.com/blog.vrid.in/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Tax-bro.png?resize=600%2C600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/blog.vrid.in/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Tax-bro.png?resize=400%2C400&amp;ssl=1 400w, https://i0.wp.com/blog.vrid.in/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Tax-bro.png?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/blog.vrid.in/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Tax-bro.png?w=2000&amp;ssl=1 2000w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /\u003E\u003C/figure\u003E\n\n\n\n\u003Cp\u003EEvery year, when the Union Budget is announced, there&#8217;s a flurry of discussions about how it affects the economy, the markets, and most importantly, our personal finances.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\n\n\u003Cp\u003EAnd if you’ve been avoiding the “budget news” avalanche, we don’t blame you. Taxes and budget news are very overwhelming and confusing.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\n\n\u003Cp\u003EBut now that all noise is down we would like to discuss the major updates in the Budget 2025 and the brand-new Income Tax Bill which can affect your personal finance.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\n\n\u003Cp\u003ELet’s break down the most important changes from the Budget 2025, including tax slab changes, TCS adjustments, and other key updates. Then, let’s delve into the major reforms introduced by the New Income Tax Bill and how it differs from the old one. So, buckle up as we explain everything in simple terms.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\n\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cmark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#9b51e0\" class=\"has-inline-color\"\u003EEstimated read time: 3 minutes and 44 seconds\u003C/mark\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"wp-block-columns has-tertiary-background-color has-background is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-la