\" class=\"wp-block-social-link-anchor\"\u003E\u003Csvg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.1\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\"\u003E\u003Cpath d=\"M13.982 10.622 20.54 3h-1.554l-5.693 6.618L8.745 3H3.5l6.876 10.007L3.5 21h1.554l6.012-6.989L15.868 21h5.245l-7.131-10.378Zm-2.128 2.474-.697-.997-5.543-7.93H8l4.474 6.4.697.996 5.815 8.318h-2.387l-4.745-6.787Z\" /\u003E\u003C/svg\u003E\u003Cspan class=\"wp-block-social-link-label screen-reader-text\"\u003EX\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003C/ul\u003E\n\n\n\n\u003Chr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/\u003E\n\n\n\n\u003Ch2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EStill Curious?\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/h2\u003E\n\n\n\n\u003Cp\u003EIf you are like us, who likes to analyse a little more or check out content in different formats, well you are in luck. Below you can find some suitable content we found.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\n\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https://finshots.in/archive/the-budget-2025-simplified-nirmala-sitharaman-narendra-modi-india-bihar/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\"\u003EFinshots &#8211; The Budget simplified (Blog)\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\n\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https://cleartax.in/s/budget-2025-highlights#h24\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\"\u003ECleartax &#8211; Budget 2025 Highlights: PDF Download, Key Takeaways and Important Points (Blog)\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\n\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https://youtu.be/jgSD4MsGDoI?feature=shared\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\"\u003EBusiness Standard &#8211; All about the New Income Tax Bill 2025 (YT Video)\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\n\n\u003Cp\u003ENote:&nbsp;We don’t have any affiliation&nbsp;with them. We are sharing links only for educational purposes. The opinions expressed by them belong solely to them and do not reflect the views of Vrid.\u003C/p\u003E\n",
